         <div type="abstract">
            <head>Abstract</head>
            <p>Alexander II Gileberto episcopo Lundoniensi: inter alia mandat, ut summam universam censusbeati Petri in regno Anglorum debitam (Godescalco) abbati sancti Bertini (Saint-Bertin, D. Thérouanne) transmittat. (- Saepe nobisa).<list>
                  <item>[Listeneintrag 1]</item>
               </list></p>
         </div>

